================================================================================
  stealth-vps — generated credentials and connection details
================================================================================
Managed by Ansible for host: {{ ansible_facts.hostname }}.
Do not edit by hand — values are re-rendered on the next playbook run.
Check the file mtime with `stat /root/stealth-vps-credentials.txt` to see when
this was last refreshed.

================================================================================
  3X-UI panel
================================================================================
{% if stealth_vps_panel_state is defined %}
{# panel scheme is detected by tasks/panel.yml (HTTPS first, HTTP fallback) #}
{# and persisted as the fact stealth_vps_panel_scheme. When the credentials  #}
{# file is rendered without panel.yml having run this session, fall back to  #}
{# the legacy "domain → https else http" heuristic.                          #}
{% set scheme = stealth_vps_panel_scheme | default('https' if stealth_vps_domain else 'http') %}
{% set host_direct = stealth_vps_domain if stealth_vps_domain else (ansible_facts.default_ipv4.address | default(ansible_facts.fqdn)) %}
URL (via SSH tunnel — recommended; the panel port is closed by UFW
unless `stealth_hardening_ufw_expose_panel=true`):
    ssh -i <your-key> -p {{ stealth_hardening_ssh_port | default(22550) }} \
        -L 8888:localhost:{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }} \
        root@{{ ansible_facts.default_ipv4.address | default(ansible_facts.fqdn) }}
    Then open: {{ scheme }}://localhost:8888/{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/

URL (direct — only reachable when UFW is disabled or panel exposed):
    {{ scheme }}://{{ host_direct }}:{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }}/{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/

Username:      {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.username }}
Password:      {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.password }}
Port:          {{ stealth_vps_panel_state.port }}
Base path:     /{{ stealth_vps_panel_state.web_base_path }}/
TLS:           {{ "Let's Encrypt (CN=" + stealth_vps_domain + ")" if stealth_vps_domain else "none (HTTP only)" }}
Service:       systemctl status x-ui
{% else %}
Pending — populated by the panel task on the next playbook run.
{% endif %}

