================================================================================
  Hysteria2
================================================================================
{% if stealth_vps_hysteria_state is defined %}
{% set hy_host = stealth_vps_domain if stealth_vps_domain else (ansible_facts.default_ipv4.address | default(ansible_facts.fqdn)) %}
{% set hy_sni = stealth_vps_domain if stealth_vps_domain else stealth_vps_hysteria_cert_cn %}
{% set hy_insecure_flag = '' if stealth_vps_domain else '&insecure=1' %}
{% set hy_tls_label = "Let's Encrypt (CN=" + stealth_vps_domain + ")" if stealth_vps_domain else "self-signed (CN=" + stealth_vps_hysteria_cert_cn + ") — clients must set insecure=1" %}
{% set hy_port_suffix = ',' + (stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping_min | string) + '-' + (stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping_max | string) if stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping else '' %}
Port (UDP):    {{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.port }}{{ ' (+ hopping range ' + (stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping_min | string) + '-' + (stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping_max | string) + ')' if stealth_vps_hysteria_port_hopping else '' }}
SNI:           {{ hy_sni }}
Auth password: {{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.auth_password }}
Obfs type:     salamander
Obfs password: {{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.obfs_password }}
Masquerade:    {{ stealth_vps_hysteria_masquerade_url }}
TLS:           {{ hy_tls_label }}
Service:       systemctl status hysteria-server

Connection URI — paste into a Hysteria2-aware client (NekoBox, Hiddify, sing-box, official hysteria client):

    hysteria2://{{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.auth_password }}@{{ hy_host }}:{{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.port }}{{ hy_port_suffix }}/?obfs=salamander&obfs-password={{ stealth_vps_hysteria_state.obfs_password }}&sni={{ hy_sni }}{{ hy_insecure_flag }}#{{ stealth_vps_hysteria_remark }}
{% else %}
Pending — populated by the hysteria task on the next playbook run.
{% endif %}
